# Competency question: "What aboutness modes can an information carrier bear
# toward its subject — and is the mention/use space spanned with no privileged
# winner?"
# Expected: exactly purrdf:aboutnessDescribes (mention: reports, quotes, depicts,
# analyzes) and purrdf:aboutnessEnacts (use: performs, demands, exemplifies,
# embodies) — the fourth domain-free epistemic axis (#349, EPIC #348). Text
# about deception is not text that deceives.

PREFIX purrdf: <https://blackcatinformatics.ca/purrdf/>

SELECT ?mode WHERE {
    ?mode a purrdf:AboutnessMode .
}
ORDER BY ?mode
